N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 23.3 - Target price

State Regulations

For purposes of distributing the State funding provided by
chapter 57 of the Laws of 2007, the target price shall be the price that
results in the payment rate to eligible producers in accordance with the
formula set forth in subdivision one of Agriculture and Markets Law, section
258-p p. Notes
